name: LAYERS
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - All the many strands informing.

When you see a mushroom it’s just a tiny part of what’s going on. Underneath the ground there are filaments that connect and expand across the entire forest nourishing and feeding. 

The mushroom is a sign of the deep vast network below. 

What pops up on the surface is the result of everything that’s gone on underneath. There are vast layers that you cannot see or feel but they are there and they are happening. 

The expansiveness and the unseen workings are there in you.

You have put information in and have grown a life. In nature we see very clearly the connectedness of everything, the flower chooses its colour to attract the bee and the bee pollinates the flower.

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
